%C3%B4-ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-Apyex3TmF_rPxiy1ojJ2tg">Niệm nô kiều - 念奴嬌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trinh-Khanh/Quan-v%C5%A9-ca/poem-zOCTT5itPyfl2LeeRaK0aQ">Quan vũ ca - 觀舞歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trinh-Khanh/author-Ilze63P8CwiNVC4ocnEpgg">Từ Trinh Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Lu%C3%A2n/S%C6%A1n-trung/poem-X7RhZDfGI9R2Dp8whgCyug">Sơn trung - 山中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Lu%C3%A2n/author-VVZ_VDVd2wfprGEnIm6L6g">Lư Luân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%E1%BB%B6/Tr%C3%BAc-T%C3%A2y-xu%C3%A2n-du-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-icYfMtl0UFOyMa4rpZG16w">Trúc Tây xuân du khúc kỳ 2 - 竹西春遊曲其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%E1%BB%B6/author-AwmtxAvU68PUawMGR0lmaw">Ngô Ỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-h%E1%BA%ADu-v%C3%A3n-t%C3%ACnh-t%E1%BB%A9-s%C6%A1n-giai-thanh-duy-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-S%C6%A1n-to%C3%A0n-b%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-EaKPWD2I71atervoOnhVGA">Tuyết hậu vãn tình, tứ sơn giai thanh, duy Đông Sơn toàn bạch - 雪後晚晴四山皆青惟東山全白</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br></div>	</div>
